"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.6.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.6.4</span> 标题：楼上的房间、楼房、屋顶的房间（upper room, roof chamber）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֲלִיָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘aliyah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20\">JDG 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:23\">JDG 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:24\">JDG 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:25\">JDG 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:1\">2SA 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:23\">1KI 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:11\">2KI 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:12\">2KI 23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:11\">1CH 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:9\">2CH 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31\">NEH 3:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:32\">NEH 3:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:3\">PSA 104:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:14\">JER 22:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">兰：עִלִּי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘ili)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:11\">DAN 6:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַעֲלָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ma‘alah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:6\">AMO 9:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἀνάγαιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：anagaion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:15\">MRK 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:12\">LUK 22:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ὑπερῷον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：huperōion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:13\">ACT 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:37\">ACT 9:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:39\">ACT 9:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:8\">ACT 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob3:10\">TOB 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob3:17\">TOB 3:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0032_house_upperroom.png\" alt=\"带上层房间的房子\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">带上层房间的房子 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>楼上的房间是指在底层（地面层）上面一层的房间（该层在美式英语中为第二层，在其他大多数语言中为第一层）。楼上房间通常不会占整个楼层的面积，而是只占屋顶的一部分。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20\">JDG 3:20</a> 中，希伯来文短语<em>‘aliyath mqerah</em> （在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:24\">JDG 3:24</a> 中也叫做<em>cheder mqerah</em> ）指专门为乘凉而建造的一间楼房。由于位置比较高，所以风相对较大，而且可能是朝北的，因此受到的日晒较少。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:6\">1KI 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:8\">1KI 6:8</a> 提到围绕圣殿外侧建造的二楼和三楼（美式英语）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:8\">1KI 6:8</a> 指的是“中间层的入口”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 直译）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Hebrew Old Testament Text Project (UBS)\">HOTTP</abbr> 对此提出以下注解：“这些楼层可能是 开放式 的拱廊或走廊。因此，经文可以不必提到开放式的地面层的入口，但有必要提到第一（或中间）和第二（或最高）层的入口。”这个注解是根据希伯来文本得出的结论，因为经文清楚提到中间层有入口，并且有楼梯通向中间层，又从中间层上到顶层。然而，《七十士译本》和一个古老的犹太亚兰文译本（《他尔根》）都认为，在第8节末尾出现了两次的希伯来文形容词<em>tikonah</em> （“中间”）都是指中间层；但是，第一次其实是指最下面一层。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 赞同这个意见，英文意为：“通往最下层的入口是在殿的右边转角；通过一条螺旋楼梯上到中间层，再从中间层上到第三层。”</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:3\">PSA 104:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a> ：希伯来文<em>‘aliyoth</em> 在这些经文中指上帝的居所。许多译本都没有按字面翻译。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 在两处都译为“home”（“家”），而<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在第3节译为“home”（“家”），在第13节译为“the sky”（“天”）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 分别译为“palace”（“宫殿”）和“halls”（“大厅”）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
